        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 180°C/ 160°C (fan)/ gas 4</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1841.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
