            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Reduce the heat to medium, then add the <strong>Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>crème fraîche</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>goats' cheese </strong>(you will use the rest for garnish!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
