      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained spaghetti</strong> to the pan with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a grind of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Stir it all together until the sauce begins to stick to the spaghetti – this is your <strong>goats' cheese & mushroom spaghetti</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
